#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn48.71-82"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn48.71-82:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.71-82:0.2"
msgid "8. Gaṅgāpeyyālavagga "
msgstr "8. Abbreviated Texts on the Ganges "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 71–82. Pācīnādisutta → pācīnaninnādisuttāni (bj) | viveka (pts1)
msgctxt "sn48.71-82:0.3"
msgid "71–82. Pācīnādisutta "
msgstr "71–82. Slanting East, Etc. "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn48.71-82:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, gaṅgā nadī pācīnaninnā pācīnapoṇā pācīnapabbhārā; "
msgstr "“Mendicants, the Ganges river slants, slopes, and inclines to the east. "

msgctxt "sn48.71-82:1.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pañcindriyāni bhāvento pañcindriyāni bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro. "
msgstr "In the same way, a mendicant developing and cultivating the five faculties slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.71-82:1.3"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pañcindriyāni bhāvento pañcindriyāni bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro? "
msgstr "How so? "

msgctxt "sn48.71-82:1.4"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu saddhindriyaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ, "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops the faculties of faith, "

msgctxt "sn48.71-82:1.5"
msgid "vīriyindriyaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "energy, "

msgctxt "sn48.71-82:1.6"
msgid "satindriyaṃ … "
msgstr "mindfulness, "

msgctxt "sn48.71-82:1.7"
msgid "samādhindriyaṃ … "
msgstr "immersion, "

msgctxt "sn48.71-82:1.8"
msgid "paññindriyaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ. "
msgstr "and wisdom, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen as letting go. "

msgctxt "sn48.71-82:1.9"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pañcindriyāni bhāvento pañcindriyāni bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant developing and cultivating the five faculties slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.71-82:1.10"
msgid "Dvādasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.71-82:1.11"
msgid "Gaṅgāpeyyālavaggo aṭṭhamo. "
msgstr "(To be expanded for each of the different rivers as in SN 45.91–102.) "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.240, sc2
msgctxt "sn48.71-82:2.1"
msgid "Cha pācīnato ninnā, "
msgstr "Six on slanting to the east, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn48.71-82:2.2"
msgid "cha ninnā ca samuddato; "
msgstr "and six on slanting to the ocean; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn48.71-82:2.3"
msgid "Dvete cha dvādasa honti, "
msgstr "these two sixes make twelve, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn48.71-82:2.4"
msgid "vaggo tena pavuccatīti. "
msgstr "and that’s how this chapter is recited."

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
